     I                                        1   5 A2BHB1
     I                                        6  10 A2BHB2
     I                                       11  12 A2BHB3
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 B2BHB
     I                                        1   5 B2BHB1
     I                                        6  10 B2BHB2
